Class XmlRpcResultFileMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.seagate.util.Message

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class XmlRpcResultFileMessage
extends XmlRpcMessage
    Result file message. The inbound message is simply a dictionary in form of (Python notation): {'tag' : 'RESULT_FILE', 'data' : {'cellIndex' : 0, 'trayIndex' : 0, 'timestamp' : 1.111, 'resultFileTag' : 'msg', 'resultFileData' : xmlrpclib.Binary('blah')}}
